Name: Coin Pusher
About the game: Find the most addictive funfair machine and become the new king of Coin Pusher! The principle is simple, add coins on the deck and drop a maximum of bonuses and gifts into the basket! Dropping coins will allow you to gain levels! Choose from one of the 5 available themes and start your climb to riches! Features: ■ Different prizes to collect and sell! ■ Many different pieces! ■ 5 different themes with different speed trays! ■ Level system! ■ Coins generator! ■ Good music!
